CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 31, 1959, pg. 27 reads: "Makes Comeback - Since losing its first two games of the season in CIty League cage play, Westinghouse High School has gone undefeated in five straight games. Pacing the Bulldogs' attack are, left to right, Verner Russell, Ronald Henderson, Anthony Liscib, Adrien Page and Rodger Parris. - Harris PHoto."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of five Westinghouse basketball players, left to right, Verner Russell, Ronald Henderson, Anthony Liscib, Adrien Page, and Rodger Parrish
